Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.59,0:00:17.94,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.59,0:00:17.94,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fscy80\fscx120}{\pos(478,455)}{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.09,0:00:27.74,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此所談到的未來  就是有你陪伴的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.27,0:00:31.37,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh baby I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.27,0:00:31.37,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fscy80\fscx120}{\pos(519,455)}{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.52,0:00:35.04,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願意成為妳的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.73,0:00:43.26,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅信彼此牽在一起的雙手  發誓就這樣走下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.32,0:00:50.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我討厭你"這句話 即使是玩笑話我也不忍出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.08,0:00:57.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但"我喜歡你"這句話 如果不是事實我也不會說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.84,0:01:05.32,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像妳在無法見面時 沒有心思顧及其他一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.55,0:01:11.04,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這顆心  只屬於一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.64,0:01:15.04,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.64,0:01:15.04,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fscy80\fscx120}{\pos(478,455)}{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.19,0:01:24.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓我倆的愛分隔兩地  請你緊緊擁抱住我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.45,0:01:31.73,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如膠似漆  心緒不寧的夜晚仍會造訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.75,0:01:39.52,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那時 就更緊地 抱緊彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.26,0:22:40.95,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個星空如此閃耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.85,0:22:50.13,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些無論怎樣都是因為有了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.53,0:23:00.51,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若沒有了你 我一個人是做不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.04,0:23:11.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映在眼睛裏的東西 全都開始傾斜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.17,0:23:21.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望遼闊的天空 星星多麼閃耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.06,0:23:32.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手觸不及星星 為何天空如此遙遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.65,0:23:37.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要與你相逢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.85,0:00:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉近最喜歡與最討厭的距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.95,0:00:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兩人的推理與懸案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.65,0:00:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無人島以及深海裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.15,0:00:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南和平次的推理爆發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.35,0:00:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.86,0:00:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.76,0:00:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.25,0:01:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了參加電視臺辦的東西部偵探推理大賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和服部平次來到了沖繩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.56,0:01:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無名島據說發現過無名屍以及奇妙文字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和電視臺的人一起去無人島檢查場地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.06,0:01:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.06,0:02:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視臺的職員平良伊江小姐遇害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.87,0:02:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體旁留下了匪夷所思的訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.57,0:02:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且來時的船以及船長亦隨之消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.65,0:02:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤島的公主與龍宮城(追求篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.15,0:02:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 船錨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.96,0:02:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平良小姐潛水的那片海底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有這種東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.56,0:02:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錨鏈斷了 上頭遍體鱗傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.97,0:02:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.97,0:02:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是一年前死者所遺的船錨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.07,0:02:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.37,0:02:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人坐船到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.17,0:02:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這幢房子躲避颱風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.08,0:02:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果船錨斷了 船漂走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.65,0:02:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錨鏈上沾滿了貝殼和海藻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.05,0:02:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海裏的樣子應該有四、五年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.35,0:02:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四、五年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.06,0:02:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像就是那件事情發生的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.76,0:03:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長家裏續發事件的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.06,0:03:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 出了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.97,0:03:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次是五年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.97,0:03:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長的獨生女都小姐被綁架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.37,0:03:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一年以後 強盜集團搶光町長的家裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長的傳家之寶金色屏風被搶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.55,0:03:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長和管家與犯人通過電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.65,0:03:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據他們說綁架犯跟搶劫犯似乎是同夥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來呢 那些犯人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.16,0:03:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贖回女兒以及屏風的錢町長都沒有付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.26,0:03:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼不了了之了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.67,0:03:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說小姐跟屏風都失蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.37,0:03:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長還真不容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.57,0:03:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件發生的時候 他的妻子剛剛去世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.48,0:03:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個女僕被強盜夥子殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.35,0:03:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家也嚇得提出辭呈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長因為沒有付錢贖人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.85,0:04:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被傳說是冷血動物而倍受譴責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.86,0:04:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長後來在島上又發現餓死的無名屍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.26,0:04:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那根柱子上的奇怪文字後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.56,0:04:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上這回的殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.57,0:04:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人覺得他是不是被古索的使者附身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.67,0:04:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得刻在柱子上的文字是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.98,0:04:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主沉睡之處是"甲"而非"乙"是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.25,0:04:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個公主是不是指被綁架的小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.06,0:04:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 那個小姐已經被殺害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被埋在這島上的什麼地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.36,0:04:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 她變成了異世界的使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加害了平良小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.87,0:04:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕異世界之使者的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這把刀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.28,0:05:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據古老傳說 女生為了防止魂魄被吸走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.85,0:05:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就咬著小刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也可以用來防身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.76,0:05:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.06,0:05:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個茶碗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.06,0:05:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被誰當過煙灰缸用過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.37,0:05:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面有好幾種煙頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.27,0:05:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且碗裏滅火用的水還沒有完全乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.88,0:05:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之 在我們之前有人來過這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.25,0:05:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有群來路不明的人在這裏聚集過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.45,0:05:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了什麼事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.85,0:05:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能不只一兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了一個女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.26,0:05:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正潛藏在這座小島上的某處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.76,0:05:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自封"古索使者"的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.26,0:05:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害平良小姐的犯人的同夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的就在這座小島上嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.37,0:06:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這只是推測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.27,0:06:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好正在伺機攻擊我們也不一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.38,0:06:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取走我們所有人的靈魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來  他們會不會已經埋伏在這屋子裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.45,0:06:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.85,0:06:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏除了我們沒有別人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.36,0:06:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這房子的玻璃碎了不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.46,0:06:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁我們談話的時候 悄悄潛入這裏也是很容易的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.07,0:06:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們再分頭仔細搜查一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.57,0:06:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏恐懼乾等也無濟於事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 久米先生 池間先生 大東先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二樓就拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於我們就和竹富先生在一樓逛逛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.05,0:06:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.65,0:06:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你一個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.26,0:06:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事的話挺危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被保護的是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳會空手道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.47,0:07:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.67,0:07:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在東京大會上贏過冠軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是合氣道二段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼全靠你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人來的話就交給我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.75,0:07:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大叔和咱們一起來是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 看上去最沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.26,0:07:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 服部 這是最後的房間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少裝模作樣的  快點開門吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.67,0:07:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.18,0:07:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有人在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.45,0:07:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似沒有人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.35,0:07:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和其他房間相比 這間房間還真大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.96,0:08:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏可能原來是町長和太太住的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.26,0:08:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 町長夫婦的相片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長太太真是漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.57,0:08:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼 平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.67,0:08:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼裝了兩張照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.95,0:08:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長和年輕女性的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.75,0:08:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這個町長有外遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.76,0:08:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是町長的獨生女都小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得很像町長太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.36,0:08:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮膚白晰 個性溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.16,0:08:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家都在猜想她會嫁給誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是誰也想不到五年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.07,0:08:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她才在上大學的時候被綁架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.67,0:08:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.78,0:08:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你是從九州電視臺過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼對這件事情這麼清楚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.35,0:09:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在町長家做女傭的松本嘉子是我的表妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.66,0:09:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她經常跟我說這些事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女傭是不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶劫時遇害的那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.47,0:09:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前的那次事件裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.57,0:09:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被強盜集團的其中一人殺害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起表兄妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.37,0:09:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池間先生的母親以及町長太太是姊妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐則是他的表親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.45,0:09:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片上的城堡沒有見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.15,0:09:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在哪裡的建築
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.15,0:09:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是城堡 是町長的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.36,0:09:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常豪華的房屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.36,0:09:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽嘉子說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.36,0:09:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房子蓋好後 當時還很小的都小姐也很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.07,0:09:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是城堡裏的公主一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.17,0:09:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.17,0:09:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根柱子上刻的公主果然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指都小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.98,0:10:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根柱子上也刻了奇怪的文字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.05,0:10:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是那位小姐寫的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.55,0:10:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧 有三處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.66,0:10:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是用蠟筆寫上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.36,0:10:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最上面的是"千代哥哥"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.37,0:10:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下方二十公分處是寫"媽咪"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.87,0:10:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最下面是"我"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.27,0:10:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我"附近有許多條橫線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.18,0:10:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來應該是小姐小時候比身高用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.95,0:10:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是身高啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.55,0:10:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過"媽咪"指的是母親吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.25,0:10:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐為什麼要這樣寫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.56,0:10:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 "媽咪"好像不是指母親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.76,0:10:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這裏 雖然有點淡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.36,0:10:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間的門上也用蠟筆寫了字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.37,0:10:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.77,0:10:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.37,0:11:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.88,0:11:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個"媽咪"和"千代哥哥"是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.98,0:11:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是小姐的同學呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.55,0:11:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐還那麼小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.05,0:11:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有那麼高的同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.75,0:11:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.36,0:11:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的門也寫著"媽咪"和"千代哥哥"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.06,0:11:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說那邊是"千代哥哥"的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間就是"媽咪"的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.97,0:11:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.47,0:11:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文字旁邊還有奇怪的畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"媽咪"的旁邊是鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.57,0:11:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"千代哥哥"的旁邊好像是鰻魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.38,0:11:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在這麼昏暗的地方看小孩子的畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.15,0:11:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是恐怖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.65,0:11:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 無人島上有這樣的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.75,0:11:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說明了"媽咪"和"千代哥哥"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.19,0:11:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是和小姐常來這一帶的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 只有等救援來了 在救我們回島上後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.66,0:12:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再問問町長 這兩個人是誰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.87,0:12:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能和這殺人事件有關聯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.17,0:12:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.78,0:12:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是久米先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二樓是不是出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.55,0:12:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說犯人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.35,0:12:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.56,0:12:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 出了什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.16,0:12:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人出現了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.56,0:12:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.97,0:12:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子突然大叫然後跌倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.37,0:12:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自看到了牆上吊著的那幅畫以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.28,0:12:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幅畫是都小姐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.65,0:12:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶 跟剛才的照片一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.15,0:12:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該是太太畫的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.55,0:12:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽嘉子說太太擅長繪畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.76,0:12:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.96,0:13:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的表妹 町長家的女傭就是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.37,0:13:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來這裏和町長家有關係的人有四個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.07,0:13:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽是町長太太的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.38,0:13:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹富和女傭是表兄妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.95,0:13:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久米自從國小後跟都小姐一直是同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.45,0:13:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大東先生據說和町長太太從小就認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.66,0:13:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小就認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.46,0:13:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年我跟我媽去給町長夫人掃墓的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.46,0:13:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽問他是誰的時候 他說是從小跟太太就認識的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.17,0:13:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽說不認識你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.87,0:13:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不是真的就不得而知了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.48,0:13:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽跟太太的年齡差遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.05,0:13:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽是太太的妹妹的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.55,0:13:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也來過這個島吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.95,0:14:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.75,0:14:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座島跟町長家 我之前都沒有來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.16,0:14:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長是有錢人 門檻高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.66,0:14:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連小姐也只是幼時看過一眼而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.36,0:14:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼久米先生看了小姐畫會感到驚嚇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.67,0:14:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能是覺得小姐的靈魂出來了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.57,0:14:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為傳言中的小姐已經遇害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.65,0:14:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.05,0:14:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房子應該是沒有藏匿可疑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.15,0:14:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家集合到樓下的房間裏等待救援吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這未免太久了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.97,0:15:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔八成又在哪跟女郎喝酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.85,0:15:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個白癡大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.25,0:15:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.56,0:15:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.66,0:15:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是救援船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.76,0:15:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.27,0:15:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那船有點怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.77,0:15:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有燈亮 停靠的方式也頗奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.76,0:15:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手法真殘忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.86,0:15:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人用水管之類的硬物反覆毆打船長後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎死後還在打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.77,0:16:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把船長掛在船頭上再寫上那幾個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.08,0:16:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我乃古索的使者"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.95,0:16:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有恨到極點才會這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 到底是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.65,0:16:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這島上除了我們以外還有其他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.26,0:16:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在等著殺害我們的殺人狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.96,0:16:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.76,0:16:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船撞到棧橋的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.97,0:16:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都在那幢房子裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.37,0:16:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱這艘船的犯人應該就在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.58,0:16:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自封"古索使者"的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.65,0:16:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.45,0:16:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我看了一下船裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.35,0:16:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長座位邊有個像是小型電視的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.56,0:16:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了上面的雷達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.86,0:16:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船好像只是一直繞著島航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.76,0:17:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 自動駕駛儀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個的話沒有人也可以操縱船的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海裏的潮流也是會有影響的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.27,0:17:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用自動駕駛把船正好開到棧橋這來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.25,0:17:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 設定仔細就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.95,0:17:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動駕駛會因潮流影響的誤差大約是50-100尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.16,0:17:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說設置時緊貼著岸邊行駛的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.96,0:17:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿著海岸的珊瑚礁走就可以碰到棧橋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.97,0:17:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看 船的側面有著擦撞的痕跡對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.07,0:17:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是擦撞到珊瑚礁行駛的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.98,0:17:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之 利用自動駕駛 幾個小時前把船開出棧橋的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.85,0:17:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個犯罪手法就成立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在島上的我們也能做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.75,0:17:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂… 難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.06,0:18:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之中可能藏有犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.06,0:18:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們四個人為了尋找平良小姐離開船時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.57,0:18:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是說也跟著下船了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.77,0:18:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時在船上的最後一個人就可以趁機把船長殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.68,0:18:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.15,0:18:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是最後一個下船的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.35,0:18:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…難道是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.15,0:18:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是自我下船後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.16,0:18:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都可以偷偷回去 一樣可以行兇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.86,0:18:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 你沒忘記吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探小哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.66,0:18:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平良小姐出事的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.77,0:18:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 你不是說了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.97,0:18:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平良小姐旁邊沙灘上寫的字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.98,0:18:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家當時都還在島的另一邊 不可能寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.85,0:18:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那行字是在滿潮線的下方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.35,0:19:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不趕在平良小姐稍早前抵達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.65,0:19:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海浪就會沖走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.26,0:19:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確實說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.76,0:19:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而…而且 這跟平良小姐、船長出事時寫的字一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.16,0:19:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明兇手是同一個人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.57,0:19:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來 我們之中就不可能有犯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.87,0:19:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若犯人不只一個的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.17,0:19:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之中就有可能有共犯 替他寫了同樣的文字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.18,0:19:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這字也可能是犯人設下的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.85,0:19:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們以為犯人在我們之中  而起內鬨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 船回來了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.86,0:19:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 有什麼事回去的話再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.36,0:19:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 船長被放下來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.86,0:19:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看就已經沒有燃料了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還不只這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.87,0:19:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無線電也被破壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.77,0:19:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的行李也都不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.87,0:19:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.88,0:20:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人要把我們困在島上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.05,0:20:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能還有什麼事要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.65,0:20:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.55,0:20:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要殺人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.25,0:20:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想被殺的話 最好先待在剛才的房子裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.26,0:20:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著救援前來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.36,0:20:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.26,0:20:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到什麼時候救援船才會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.87,0:20:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.37,0:20:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 平次 我們也先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.88,0:20:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.08,0:20:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.15,0:20:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤  這件案子很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的被害人平良小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.45,0:20:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體很仔細地放好雙手 眼睛也是闔上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.46,0:20:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是船長卻是被毆打致死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.86,0:20:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人可能不是同一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是這樣還是差太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.97,0:20:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我最在意的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.07,0:21:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被殺害前船長跟平良小姐的舉動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.78,0:21:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平良小姐特地去有激流的海域潛水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.75,0:21:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長則是直到預定時間為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在島上繞來繞去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.35,0:21:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船上的海底探測器也是開著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.26,0:21:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像大家都在找什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.36,0:21:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是我在海底看見的那個船錨的錨鏈捆住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.66,0:21:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某樣東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.57,0:21:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.87,0:21:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才待的那個房間椅子的背面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.67,0:21:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有蠟筆寫過的孩子字跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.18,0:21:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坐的字背面寫的是"我"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.58,0:21:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭的椅子是"媽媽"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.95,0:21:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤 但我坐的椅子背面是"金城先生"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.85,0:21:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是小姐寫的字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.46,0:21:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過金城先生不是她的父親嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.96,0:21:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不寫"爸爸"呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.16,0:21:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有寫字的椅子只有那三張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.87,0:22:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 都沒有和小姐比身高的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.57,0:22:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"媽咪" 和"千代哥哥"的椅子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.97,0:22:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有房間卻沒有椅子  的確很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.98,0:22:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"媽咪"和"千代哥哥"到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.17,0:23:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.87,0:23:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎餅和餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.18,0:23:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才 是什麼聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.15,0:23:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.25,0:23:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是水滴下來的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.65,0:24:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 朝這裏接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.96,0:24:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.36,0:24:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"古索的使者"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.96,0:24:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.56,0:24:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤島的公主與龍宮城(解決篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.47,0:24:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.67,0:24:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.87,0:24:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次終於是解決篇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.58,0:24:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是你
